title: Gibby Miller from DAIS Records, Panic and The Trouble
itunes:title: Gibby Miller from DAIS Records, Panic and The Trouble
description:
Let's get you acquainted with the man behind DAIS Records, Gibby Miller. He also sang for some great punk/hardcore bands called Panic and The Trouble (both from Boston). We dive deep into growing up in the midwest, the legend of Makeoutclub.com (he was the founder!) and of course the Boston scene. Enjoy! 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
